      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels different though. it's not just a mistake or a bad day. it's like the foundation is just gone. everything that made me... me... it's all gone. i'm just standing here looking at this empty space where a person used to be. how can i even keep going when that person doesn't exist anymore? it feels like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life.",
